ce":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2919137286/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2919137286","tinyui":"/x/BoD_rQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2919137286","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2919137286/C+mo+Maximizar+la+Eficiencia+de+Jira","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2919137286"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"16c8f939-1b35-4b3f-8bbe-08d19e17786e\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Los Releases / Versiones son una utilidad que nos ofrece Jira para identificar distintos momentos dentro del proyecto. Estas nos ayudan a organizar el trabajo proporcion&aacute;ndonos puntos de partida y llegada a los que debemos aspirar.</p><p>Para esto, nos da la opci&oacute;n de asignar distintos Tickets / Indicentes a las versiones creadas</p><p>Release = Versi&oacute;n</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p /><h3>I. Habilitar la funcion Releases en la configuraci&oacute;n del Proyecto</h3><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Desde el men&uacute; izquierdo de nuestro tablero vamos a <em>Configuraci&oacute;n de Proyecto </em>⚙️</p></li><li><p>Seleccionamos <em>Features</em></p></li><li><p>Habilitamos la funcion <em>Releases</em></p></li></ol><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1642\" ac:original-width=\"2880\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20240404-191806.png\" ac:width=\"760\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20240404-191806.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><h3>II. Crear una versi&oacute;n / release en Jira</h3><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Abrir proyecto</p></li><li><p>En el men&uacute; izquierdo del proyecto, seleccionar <em>Releases (versiones).</em></p></li><li><p>Seleccionar la opci&oacute;n <em>Crear versi&oacute;n</em></p></li><li><p>Completar los datos. El nombre puede ser un nombre de clave interno, pero generalmente es un valor num&eacute;rico, por ejemplo 1.0, 2.1.1, etc.</p></li></ol><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"d0574d31-8dd2-43f8-9c88-e875f9567d73\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Al crear la versi&oacute;n / release, se van a crear dos campos.</p><ul><li><p><em><strong>Affect Version </strong></em>&rarr; Este campo es b&aacute;sicamente para seleccionar de que versi&oacute;n result&oacute; un bug encontrado.</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Fix Version </strong></em>&rarr;<em><strong> </strong></em>Este es el campo m&aacute;s importante, que identifica dentro en que versi&oacute;n se va a publicar esta tarea. Nos va a ayudar para la planificaci&oacute;n de los deploys, la supervisi&oacute;n del progreso y de la velocidad, y se utiliza tambi&eacute;n para la generaci&oacute;n de reportes.</p></li></ul></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><a href=\"https://www.atlassian.com/es/agile/tutorials/versions\" data-card-appearance=\"block\">https://www.atlassian.com/es/agile/tutorials/versions</a><a href=\"https://support.atlassian.com/jira-software-cloud/docs/enable-releases-and-versions/\" data-card-appearance=\"block\">https://support.atlassian.com/jira-software-cloud/docs/enable-releases-and-versions/</a>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2995027970"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":5},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2995027970/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2995027970/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2995027970/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2995027970/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2995027970","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2995027970/Releases+Versiones","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2995027970","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2995027970","tinyui":"/x/AoCEsg","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}